<section id="contact" class="py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12 text-center" style="background: var(--color-accent);">
  <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto">

    <p class="font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4 text-white/60" style="font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 30px);">
      <span data-fr>Vous avez un projet ?</span><span data-en>Have a project?</span>
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-[clamp(32px,6vw,60px)] text-white leading-[1.05] mb-6">
      <span data-fr>Travaillons ensemble.</span><span data-en>Let's work together.</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="text-[16px] text-white/75 leading-[1.7] mb-8">
      <span data-fr>Peu importe votre secteur, j'ai probablement déjà construit quelque chose de similaire. Discutons sur LinkedIn.</span>
      <span data-en>Whatever your industry, I've probably built something similar. Let's chat on LinkedIn.</span>
    </p>

    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/quentin-anvo"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg bg-white font-display font-bold text-[18px] no-underline hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
      style="color: var(--color-accent); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);"
    >
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/>
      </svg>
      <span data-fr>Me contacter sur LinkedIn</span>
      <span data-en>Contact me on LinkedIn</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
